    <div class="umang-steps">
        <div class="stage-process">
            <h4>5-Stage process for creation of social norms</h4>
            <p>
                The essence of Project Umang lies in confronting the deeply engrained & regressive social norm around
                child/early marriage and negotiating a normative shift within families, communities & system-level
                through mothers and members of women’s collectives. Hence, the Umang model has adopted a measurable
                and scalable approach for facilitating normative shift in alignment with <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="modal-open2">
                    Cristina
                    Bicchieri’s
                </a>
                <a href="https://bit.ly/45ml1Li" target="_blank">
                    <span class="highlights2">
                        5 step process for
                        creation of social norms.
                    </span>
                </a>
            </p>
            <div class="steps">
                <div class="step1" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-duration="1500">
                    <img src="~/Content/images/belief.png" alt="personal belief">
                    <p>Change in factual and normative personal belief</p>
                </div>
                <div class="step-arrow" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-duration="1500"></div>
                <div class="step2" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-duration="1500">
                    <img src="~/Content/images/directon.png" alt="personal belief">
                    <p>Collective decision to change</p>
                </div>
                <div class="step-arrow" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-duration="1500"></div>
                <div class="step3" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-duration="1500">
                    <img src="~/Content/images/non-compliance.png" alt="personal belief">
                    <p>Introduction of sanctions for non-compliance</p>
                </div>
                <div class="step-arrow" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-duration="1500"></div>
                <div class="step4" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-duration="1500">
                    <img src="~/Content/images/balance.png" alt="personal belief">
                    <p>Creation of normative expectations</p>
                </div>
                <div class="step-arrow" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-duration="1500"></div>
                <div class="step5" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-duration="1500">
                    <img src="~/Content/images/search.png" alt="personal belief">
                    <p>Creation of empirical expectations</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
